It is autumn of 48 BC, in Alexandria.

00:07:01.826 --> 00:07:09.046
Caesar has arrived, the most powerful man in Rome, and he is in the royal palace, surrounded

00:07:09.256 --> 00:07:16.106
by forces loyal to Ptolemy XIII, Cleopatra’s brother, who is plotting to get rid of his sister.

