it more bluntly, that he was known to sleep with anyone he could, and she rightfully

00:07:57.736 --> 00:08:03.036
thought that he could be a useful ally at a dangerous time for the young queen.

00:08:04.116 --> 00:08:10.096
After all, he was the most powerful man in Rome, perhaps even in the world at that time,

00:08:10.486 --> 00:08:16.816
and with his help she could get rid of her pesky little brother and secure her rule.

00:08:17.906 --> 00:08:24.776
So, in she came, reportedly wrapped up in a carpet, or camouflaged in a laundry basket.

00:08:25.766 --> 00:08:27.636
