00:16:06.713 --> 00:16:10.483
one last time and show her that he had died honourably.

00:16:11.929 --> 00:16:16.819
Now it was up to Cleopatra to kill herself, but before

00:16:16.949 --> 00:16:20.609
she could she was detained by forces loyal to Octavian.

00:16:21.749 --> 00:16:27.069
He had grand plans to bring her to Rome and parade her around, which

00:16:27.149 --> 00:16:30.579
would have been the ultimate embarrassment for the Egyptian queen.

00:16:32.099 --> 00:16:36.029
But, as you may know, it did not end that way.

00:16:37.269 --> 00:16:42.629
Legend has it that poisonous snakes, Egyptian asps, were smuggled into

00:16:42.629 --> 00:16:46.859
where Cleopatra was being kept, and she pressed them against her breast,

00:16:47.319 --> 00:16:52.259
killing herself to avoid the humiliation that she knew was awaiting her.

00:16:53.669 --> 00:16:58.179
