00:17:14.084 --> 00:17:19.324
a needle, or something like that, and that it was not her breast but her arm.

00:17:20.667 --> 00:17:27.077
However it happened, the great queen killed herself, dead at the age of 39.

00:17:29.017 --> 00:17:35.067
In terms of her legacy, well we know her story really only through the writings of Romans,

00:17:35.437 --> 00:17:41.797
who sought to portray her as a seductress and temptress, someone who had managed to seduce

00:17:41.847 --> 00:17:47.997
two powerful Roman men and in so doing caused irreparable damage to the state of Rome.

00:17:49.527 --> 00:17:54.699
