00:17:54.699 --> 00:17:59.477
Cleopatra’s, and there is no evidence that she had any other lovers than these

00:17:59.507 --> 00:18:04.867
two, while both Caesar and Marc Antony have an extensive list of former lovers.

00:18:05.617 --> 00:18:09.337
But, of course, it is Cleopatra who is remembered as

00:18:09.357 --> 00:18:13.247
this sexual figure, while the two Roman generals are not.

